{"tid":2230314,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"【大雨警報】與冷鋒相關的強雷雨區正影響本港（2020/10/5）","createTime":"2020-10-05T00:12:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T01:44:29.000Z","uid":38255,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"db1d4f1ae0dac9420f6e3c1e3cc294ef6fe33514","tid":2230314,"uid":38255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T00:12:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><img src=\"http://x.co/wk011\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk011&h=231cb168&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"http://x.co/wk012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk012&h=31a91e86&s={SIZE}\" /> <span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><ins>大雨警報：2020年10月5日</ins></span></span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\">此帖文討論期：大雨影響完結為止</span></span></strong><br />\n【註】 發出大雨警報，表示本港大部分地區可能受持續大雨影響。 此帖文為短期性質，當取消大雨警報後會隨即停用。 為使大家有一個良好舒適的瀏覽環境，請不要使用簡體中文貼文、提及力場或洗版，謝謝合作。 請勿直接張貼會自動更新的氣象圖片，請把圖片上傳至儲存空間後再轉貼在貼文上。謝謝。 以下圖片會自動更新。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏﹏</span><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><ins>◤參考網頁</ins></span></span><br />\n◆ 實時天氣照片：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_webcam_uc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fts%2Findex_webcam_uc.htm&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=2214be8f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/ts/index_webcam_uc.htm</a><br />\n◆ 閃電戒備服務：<a href=\"http://maps.weather.gov.hk/llis/llaw_uc.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmaps.weather.gov.hk%2Fllis%2Fllaw_uc.html&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q%2F4%3D&h=e507dff6\" target=\"_blank\">http://maps.weather.gov.hk/llis/llaw_uc.html</a><br />\n◆ 閃電雷達圖像：<a href=\"http://www.hko.gov.hk/wxinfo/llis/llisradarc.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hko.gov.hk%2Fwxinfo%2Fllis%2Fllisradarc.shtml&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGP1%2FuxKlhk2BFa%2FcJox4Q