gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />6點半香港以東海域自產黃回波，直接預警式黃雨都無話唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但之後一段時間係睇唔出要出紅雨，因為就咁一波掃過應該唔會太持續，係去到差唔多8點，西貢果兩粒同本體連埋左先見到九龍仲有排落。<br />\n<br />\n所以計到盡都係0745紅雨，其實都係尷尬時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8660a1e21fb2ce84ff968860d3dc64e55c1c2a8a","tid":2230314,"uid":35730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T00:36:38.000Z","msg":"黑埋佢啦"},{"pid":"3a4307df4e0852e8abca778f7505c72972f7e9cd","tid":2230314,"uid":38255,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"631e1dbf5b4005b41b5d1107b1b1926203c9ce18","tid":2230314,"uid":38255,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T00:28:12.000Z","msg":"佢7點半先黃，真係好難8點前紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果就雷達黎睇，6點仲係乜春都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />6點半香港以東海域自產黃回波，直接預警式黃雨都無話唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但之後一段時間係睇唔出要出紅雨，因為就咁一波掃過應該唔會太持續，係去到差唔多8點，西貢果兩粒同本體連埋左先見到九龍仲有排落。<br />\n<br />\n所以計到盡都係0745紅雨，其實都係尷尬時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T00:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PckNc8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPckNc8a.jpg&h=af0a4ea6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n0736呢幅睇落係九龍準備收水，點會出紅雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tFdi4e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtFdi4e2.jpg&h=0bdc8b93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到呢個時間西貢果到同本體合左體，當交合早我地幾分鐘見到，真係頂盡0745紅雨 ，都係會慘死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3300bc54708cf5fb0d157c84d9941e1d81bd9ab","tid":2230314,"uid":54502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T00:42:46.000Z","msg":"濕撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6292bb970fb14efe8ef7e820f0939cbcd9841666","tid":2230314,"uid":230439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:01:59.000Z","msg":"8:00 唔使返學啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e411f9794f31f81c4ae55d69d752ae699a52dbc","tid":2230314,"uid":38255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:15:52.000Z","msg":"好啦，呢個紅雨係應該要出，但真係揀唔到個唔會畀人插既時間出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上 午 7 時 45 分 至 8 時 45 分 ， 本 港 各 區 均 有 閃 電 記<br />\n錄 。 各 區 錄 得 雨 量 如 下 ：<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n油 尖 旺            62 至 79 毫 米 ，<br />\n九 龍 城            49 至 78 毫 米 ，<br />\n深 水 埗            53 至 69 毫 米 ，<br />\n觀 塘                4 至 54 毫 米 ，<br />\n葵 青               12 至 52 毫 米 ，<br />\n中 西 區             6 至 50 毫 米 ，<br />\n黃 大 仙            13 至 45 毫 米 ，<br />\n離 島 區             0 至 41 毫 米 ，<br />\n西 貢                0 至 29 毫 米 ，<br />\n沙 田                0 至 22 毫 米 ，<br />\n元 朗                0 至 16 毫 米 ，<br />\n荃 灣                2 至 15 毫 米 ，<br />\n北 區                0 至 13 毫 米 ，<br />\n南 區                0 至 11 毫 米 ，<br />\n屯 門                 0 至 7 毫 米 ，<br />\n東 區                 0 至 5 毫 米 ，<br />\n大 埔                 0 至 4 毫 米 ，<br />\n灣 仔                 1 至 4 毫 米 。"},{"pid":"61f2318a4834b855386f5a087d89f1434cc5d24c","tid":2230314,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:17:46.000Z","msg":"所以應該一早7:00-7:45就直上紅雨做埋預警<br />\n咁就唔洗俾人鬧得咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faffc892dc3de644e0e0f47284a73ce09d4a28de","tid":2230314,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"61f2318a4834b855386f5a087d89f1434cc5d24c","tid":2230314,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:17:46.000Z","msg":"所以應該一早7:00-7:45就直上紅雨做埋預警<br />\n咁就唔洗俾人鬧得咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:24:11.000Z","msg":"07：00-07：30出唔係叫預警叫賭博<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n07：30-07：45出就鬧得無咁慘，但都會鬧，過去有次紅係咁上下時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最大問題係，交合07：25先上黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁真係無計了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed577b30f775611101842324256eb758f5a8915","tid":2230314,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:32:50.000Z","msg":"9:30黃雨取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50cabc5fd5131c2b3099b7637f82c23be0c5725f","tid":2230314,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://x.co/wk012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk012&h=31a91e86&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">取消大雨警報</span><br />\n<ins><span class=\"x-large\">此帖文已停用，請在以下帖文集中討論：</span></ins></span><br />\n【颱風追擊】2014號熱帶氣旋 燦鴻 CHAN-HOM（16W）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2230407\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2230407</a></strong>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"50cabc5fd5131c2b3099b7637f82c23be0c5725f","tid":2230314,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:44:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://x.co/wk012\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fx.co%2Fwk012&h=31a91e86&s={SIZE}\" /><strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">取消大雨警報</span><br />\n<ins><span class=\"x-large\">此帖文已停用，請在以下帖文集中討論：</span></ins></span><br />\n【颱風追擊】2014號熱帶氣旋 燦